Apache compatible Virtual Host utilities

Scripts to made easy virtual hosts configuration

Installation:
    Under construction !

Using under sudo:
    Cmnd_Alias ADMIN_SCRIPTS = /scripts/*


Usage Examples:

    # add a new virtual host to apache webserver
    sudo /scripts/add -u mock -d domain.com -q 1024 -p anypassword

    # add a new server alias to an existing domain
    sudo /scripts/add_alias -u mock -d domain -a alias.domain.com

    # suspend virtual host (redirects vhosts to standard suspended page)
    sudo /scripts/suspend_vhost -u mock

    # unsuspend virtual host (remove redirect)
    sudo /scripts/unsuspend_vhost -u mock
